[[File:Brilliant_missile.jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Saesee Tiin/Legends|Saesee Tiin]] stops a brilliant missile in mid-flight.]]
The '''brilliant missile''' was a variety of [[Homing missile/Legends|homing missile]] capable of tracking its targets with such precision that it could be considered [[Sentience/Legends|semi-sentient]]. The [[Vindicator XM-15 "brilliant" missile|Vindicator XM-15]] was one type of brilliant missile produced by [[Arakyd Industries/Legends|Arakyd Industries]]. The [[Coalition of Automaton Rights Activists]] called the XM-15 an abomination, and the [[Mechanical Liberation Front]] tried to free a shipment of XM-15, but blew up a 25-[[Kilometer/Legends|kilometer]] radius of [[Havridam City]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[New Bakstre]], killing 14 activists.<ref name="Hnn-Droid Rights Activists Decry Brilliant Missiles">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|51|business/13411_2.html|Droid Rights Activists Decry Brilliant Missiles}}</ref>

Brilliant missiles were known to be used by [[B3 ultra battle droid]]s during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="Heavy Metal Jedi">{{CWACite|1|Heavy Metal Jedi}}</ref><ref name="NEGD">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

